17:19.255 --> 17:20.213
- I'll talk to grandma.

17:22.041 --> 17:23.303
Maybe she could pay for it.

17:26.045 --> 17:28.003
- Wait, I wanna go to Japan too.

17:29.657 --> 17:31.354
- No, no, no, you're
you're not going with me.

17:31.398 --> 17:32.703
- Why not?

17:32.747 --> 17:34.140
- Because you're annoying.

17:34.183 --> 17:36.446
- How come always
gets what he wants?

17:36.490 --> 17:37.839
- God, you're such
a whiny little shit.

17:37.882 --> 17:38.709
- And you're a dick.

17:38.753 --> 17:40.494
- Hey, hey, hey.

17:40.537 --> 17:41.147
All right.

17:42.713 --> 17:43.453
Quit your bitching.

17:51.679 --> 17:54.073
[phone ringing]

17:58.164 --> 18:00.557
