hell was that, huh?

18:01.906 --> 18:02.777
Jerry?

18:04.996 --> 18:05.910
Jerry, you there?

18:07.695 --> 18:08.696
Hey man.

18:08.739 --> 18:11.133
[ominous music]

18:13.353 --> 18:16.138
Jerry, can you hear me?

18:20.795 --> 18:23.450
[siren wailing]

18:24.712 --> 18:27.541
[suspenseful music]

18:31.675 --> 18:33.155
He'll call back.

18:34.113 --> 18:36.767
[ominous music]

