18:53.044 --> 18:54.568
- I know, I know, I'm sorry.

18:54.611 --> 18:56.744
Is she asleep?

18:56.787 --> 18:58.528
- Yeah, she's
sleeping after a bath.

18:58.572 --> 19:00.269
