19:16.894 --> 19:18.200
- Was that a brain zap?

19:18.244 --> 19:19.419
- [Max] Mm-hmm.

19:19.462 --> 19:22.726
- [Susan] Are you gonna be okay?

19:22.770 --> 19:25.120
[Max groans]

19:26.382 --> 19:27.688
- Oh, man.

