[button clicks]

20:03.854 --> 20:05.595
- Yeah.

20:05.639 --> 20:07.945
- [Jerry] Hey, it's Jerry.

20:07.989 --> 20:10.165
Can I, can I come in?

20:11.210 --> 20:13.255
- Yeah, Jerry, come up.

20:13.299 --> 20:14.169
