30:02.061 --> 30:03.410
- Who the fuck are you?

30:03.453 --> 30:04.715
- I'm Jerry's friend.

30:04.759 --> 30:05.891
- What are you doing here?

30:05.934 --> 30:06.805
- Had no place to go.

30:08.850 --> 30:09.895
- What's in the bag?

30:12.985 --> 30:14.725
- [Big John] Take it.

30:31.525 --> 30:33.744
- What the fuck you
doing with an M68?

30:35.137 --> 30:37.313
- I just carrying them
with me for good luck.

30:37.357 --> 30:40.795
You know, as in I never know
when I'm gonna need good luck.

30:42.492 --> 30:44.103
Kind of like a
condom in my pocket.

30:45.060 --> 30:45.931
Oh, Jerry told me to give you-

30:45.974 --> 30:47.323
- Hey, hey, hey.

30:52.589 --> 30:54.461
- Jerry said, "If
anything happened to him

30:54.504 --> 30:56.158
give 'em only to you."

30:56.202 --> 30:58.769
Jerry had a bad feeling

30:58.813 --> 31:01.294
when Ellis suddenly
changed the plans.

31:01.337 --> 31:02.861
- What, what plan?

31:04.601 --> 31:06.429
Look man, I don't understand
what you're talking about.

31:06.473 --> 31:08.475
- What the fuck you
don't understand?

31:08.518 --> 31:10.781
We all in this shit
because of you bitch.

31:10.825 --> 31:12.044
- What are you talking about?

31:12.087 --> 31:14.220
- You blew his fucking cover.

31:14.263 --> 31:16.265
He was working his
way into the crew.

31:16.309 --> 31:19.181
Everything was going fine
till your dumb ass showed up.

31:19.225 --> 31:21.880
[ominous music]

31:23.969 --> 31:25.448
- It's been about
over a half hour.

31:30.671 --> 31:31.628
Should I bring him in?

31:33.848 --> 31:34.718
Okay.

31:36.416 --> 31:40.202
- The firm traffics human
organs, hearts, livers, kidneys.

31:41.682 --> 31:42.988
They dice up little kids
and sell 'em like parts

31:43.031 --> 31:45.120
for like a fucking
Toyota truck, man.

31:45.164 --> 31:46.948
We used to sell guns
for the cartels,

31:46.992 --> 31:48.732
but the cut up kids for money,

31:50.212 --> 31:51.779
that shit ain't Christian yo.

31:51.822 --> 31:52.823
[knuckles tapping]

31:52.867 --> 31:53.607
- [Vasquez] Mr. Kelly.

31:53.650 --> 31:54.913
It's Detective Vasquez.

31:56.044 --> 31:57.480
- Fuck!
- She's a cop.

31:57.524 --> 31:58.873
She can help us.

31:58.917 --> 32:01.441
Look, I'm looking for
my daughter, all right?

32:01.484 --> 32:04.096
So you're gonna tell her
everything you just told me.

32:04.139 --> 32:04.966
- We can't, man.

32:05.010 --> 32:05.793
