32:05.836 --> 32:07.490
- [Max] Why?

32:07.534 --> 32:08.927
- Because she's one of them.

32:08.970 --> 32:10.493
[knuckles tapping]

32:10.537 --> 32:13.018
- [Vasquez] Mr. Kelly, you're
not supposed to be here.

32:13.801 --> 32:14.541
- You best leave, man.

32:14.584 --> 32:15.759
