32:52.448 --> 32:54.276
- Everyone's looking for you.

32:54.320 --> 32:55.930
- I know.

32:55.974 --> 32:58.759
I came looking for the
cash to bring it to Ellis.

32:58.802 --> 33:00.456
- Oh really?

33:00.500 --> 33:02.937
[gun banging]
[Big John groans]

33:02.981 --> 33:07.768
[Big John gurgling]
[ominous music]

33:16.646 --> 33:19.301
Where is the money?

33:19.345 --> 33:24.002
- [chuckles] Get you on
the other side, bitch.

33:25.612 --> 33:27.266
[suspenseful music]
